---
title: Scallops over Creamy Chorizo Spaghetti with Bell Pepper and Parm
description: This week, our chefs have turned surf and turf on its head—in the most delicious way possible. Tender seared scallops and crispy chorizo join forces in an ultra-sophisticated and comforting pasta dish. They’re tossed with al dente spaghetti, roasted bell pepper, and a creamy, garlicky tomato sauce. One bite will have your taste buds hanging ten. See ya later, steak and shrimp!
